  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Map Movement\nTap a node to move to it.\nPay attention to node types:
    some lead to battles, others to healing or bosses.\n\nBattle Controls\nPress
    the attack button to launch an attack.\nPress the block button to protect yourself.\nTime
    your block correctly to regain some energy.\nTap on an enemy to set it as your
    current target.\n\nEnergy System\nEvery action uses energy.\nEnergy regenerates
    over time, but if it runs out you\u2019ll be limited until it recovers.\n\nEnemies\nEach
    enemy behaves differently.\nLearn their patterns and adjust your strategy to
